    </div>
    <footer>
      <nav class="footer-links">
        <a href="https://www.heavybit.com/library/podcasts/open-source-ready" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">podcast</a>
        <span class="separator">•</span>
        <a href="https://bdougie.substack.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">newsletter</a>
